      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in mint condition. It shows no meaningful signs of wear \u2014 the exterior is clean with no dents or scratches, the paint retains its original luster, and the interior is pristine throughout. Mechanically, it is in excellent working order with no known issues. A straightforward, well-maintained vehicle.",
